cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.SI

This paper focuses on the privacy and traceability of transactions in the Monero network using machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves featurization of transactions and machine learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DB (Databases). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of blockchain data, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
